FR-3.3: Run automated security checks to prevent prompt injections.   

FR-4: Document OCR
FR-4.1: Identify name, DOB, and gender from raw images.   

FR-4.3: Instantly transform Aadhaar numbers into salted SHA-256 hashes, immediately purging raw numbers from RAM.   

FR-7: Agent 4 — Document Verification
FR-7.1: Agent 4 shall verify document type from OCR output: income certificate, caste certificate, Aadhaar, disability certificate.   

FR-7.2: Agent 4 shall extract and validate issue date and expiry date from document. Output schema: {issue_date, expiry_date, is_expired, expires_within_30_days}.   

