DOC 04 — High-Level Design (HLD)
Version 4.0 — Multi-Agent Graph Orchestration
1. High-Level Architecture Overview
All real-time conversational channels (Web UI, Voice, and WhatsApp) communicate directly with the async Python FastAPI backend, which is optimized for running dynamic LangGraph execution pipelines and handling continuous WebSocket streams. This preserves the Java Spring Boot service as a blocking, transactional backend dedicated to managing data persistence, handling CRUD services, and generating PDF documents.   

